description:
Host of the Ross Tucker Football Podcast and CBS/Westwood One Color Analyst Ross Tucker joins Dan Patrick on The Dan Patrick Show to discuss the Rams' win over the Seahawks. Ross tells Dan that Russell Wilson needs to tell the Seahawks that he is their QB or get out of there.
